The paper proposes a framework for incorporating feature side-information during the learning process to improve model prediction. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper performs experiments on benchmark datasets, which suggests that it may also belong to the computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
